        <p class="text-green-700 font-medium">✓ Enrolled in TK public insurance (€110/month). Free tuition—only pays €150 semester fee. Uses English for studies, learning German on the side. Plans to stay for 18-month job search visa. Total monthly cost: ~€950.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">PhD Candidate from Brazil, 32 years old</h3>
