        <p class="text-amber-700 font-medium">△ Over 30, so public insurance unavailable. Uses Mawista private insurance (€130/month). PhD stipend covers living costs. Wishes he'd started 3 years earlier for public insurance. Still much cheaper than US PhD.</p>
